OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778767870
OL,3,CAmazon delivery driver who snatched
OL,4,Ccat from doorstep sentenced
OL,6,FAn Amazon delivery driver who was
OL,7,Fcaught on a ring doorbell stealing a
OL,8,Fcat from outside a home has been
OL,9,Fsentenced.
OL,11,FNora was taken from the garden of the
OL,12,FCrowther's family's home in Elland,
OL,13,FWest Yorkshire in January.
OL,15,FCatalin Stancu, 42, pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fstealing the cat on one of the first
OL,17,Fprosecutions under the new Pet
OL,18,FAbduction Act.
OL,20,FHe was arrested after a social media
OL,21,Fappeal.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
