OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778767870
OL,3,CAmazon delivery driver who snatched
OL,4,Ccat from doorstep sentenced
OL,6,FA registration number of Stancu's
OL,7,Fvehicle was provided by the family
OL,8,Fwhich was traced to an address in
OL,9,FOldham, where the tabby was found and
OL,10,Freunited with her family.
OL,12,FSergeant Cat Ryan said officers had
OL,13,Fbeen keen to test new legislation to
OL,14,Fbring a prosecution against Stancu, as
OL,15,Fthe new powers reflected the impact
OL,16,Fthe theft of a pet could have on
OL,17,Fvictims.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778767870
OL,3,CAmazon delivery driver who snatched
OL,4,Ccat from doorstep sentenced
OL,6,F"The loss of a pet, especially in
OL,7,Fcircumstances such as a theft, can be
OL,8,Fa huge blow for a family and this new
OL,9,Flegislation was introduced due to the
OL,10,Fseriousness of these offences.
OL,12,F"It highlights that people's dogs and
OL,13,Fcats are more than mere property, or
OL,14,Finanimate objects that can be stolen
OL,15,Fand dealt with under the theft act.
OL,17,FShe added, "It was an absolute
OL,18,Fpleasure for them to see how happy the
OL,19,FCrother's were to have her home."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
