FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778767870
OL,3,CAmazon delivery driver who snatched
OL,4,Ccat from doorstep sentenced
OL,6,FCarl Crowther, Nora's owner, said his
OL,7,Ffamily had been delighted to have
OL,8,Ftheir rescue cat returned safe and
OL,9,Fwell.
OL,11,F"The worry we all felt at losing her
OL,12,Fwas enormous as you can imagine, and
OL,13,Fwe were over the moon when we got the
OL,14,Fnews she was safe.
OL,16,F"Fortunately she has been pretty
OL,17,Foblivious to all the drama really and
OL,18,Fhas certainly settled right back in at
OL,19,Fhome. We are just grateful to have her
OL,20,Fback and see the man who stole her now
OL,21,Fdealt with through the courts."
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
