CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1778767870
OL,3,CAmazon delivery driver who snatched
OL,4,Ccat from doorstep sentenced
OL,6,FFollowing his sentencing at Bradford
OL,7,FMagistrates Court, Catalin Stancu
OL,8,Fapologised to the family.
OL,10,F"I apologise to the family for what
OL,11,Fhas happened. I've been punished
OL,12,Falready, I accept that.
OL,14,F"It was not with bad intention to take
OL,15,Fthe cat. I tried to give the cat back
OL,16,Fwhen I realise on social media. I
OL,17,Fdidn't realise the cat belonged to
OL,18,Fthem."
OL,20,FCatalin Stancu was given an eight week
OL,21,Fsuspended sentence.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
